Dam levels in Gqeberha are dangerously low again. #eNCA's Ronald Masinda covers the story. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Dam levels in Gqeberha are dangerously low again. They currently stand at just 12% full - the worst in the Nelson Mandela Bay Metro for the past eight years. READ: SA’s water crisis | Grant to help NMB avert 'Day Zero’ The recent heavy rains, despite flooding in other areas, have not helped in alleviating the scarce water challenges. Watch the video above for more details.